<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>구매 완료</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0e1c4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #945c16;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #945c16;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #b16f1f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>구매 완료!</h2>
        <p>성공적으로 구매 요청이 접수되었습니다.</p>
        <a href="/" class="button">메인 페이지로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>